-- AIRSHOW -Rolls-Royce engines to power CIT's 15 Airbus A330neos 
-- By Mark Potter
-- Wed Jul 16, 2014 07:56AM EDT
-- None



FARNBOROUGH, England, July 16 (Reuters) - U.S. aircraft leasing firm CIT Group <CIT.N> said on Wednesday it had agreed a deal for Rolls-Royce <RR.L> Trent 7000 engines to power 15 Airbus <AIR.PA> A330-900neo planes it recently ordered.

